    ReportingService
    Defines related methods for usage reporting within collaboration.
    StatisticsService
    This interface provides services for other applications using methods related to collaboration download statistics Methods of service classes can all throw the unchecked exception ServiceException if any system-level error (for example, server failure) occurs, and will in general throw a checked exception (InvalidXXXException) when an entity to be retrieved is inaccessible, instead of returning null.
